1
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,400
Brother Wang.

2
00:00:24,120 --> 00:00:26,250
I've brought the people you asked for.

3
00:00:28,480 --> 00:00:30,000
Your Chinese immortals

4
00:00:30,200 --> 00:00:31,600
aren't that impressive.

5
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:34,770
They can't even defeat a lowly executioner like you.

6
00:00:35,440 --> 00:00:37,170
Their days are truly numbered.

7
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:38,920
You Japanese woman!

8
00:00:38,920 --> 00:00:39,680
You vicious woman!

9
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:40,360
Damn you!

10
00:00:40,520 --> 00:00:41,180
Wang Shiqi,

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,520
untie us right now.

12
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:44,000
We want to fight this woman one-on-one.

13
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:44,600
Shut up.

14
00:00:46,640 --> 00:00:47,720
Cut the crap.

15
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:50,200
Hand over the two immortals,

16
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:52,600
and I'll spare your lives.

17
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:05,519
I have given you the ones you wanted.

18
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,520
Now hand my people

19
00:01:06,800 --> 00:01:07,800
over to me.

20
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,600
If you want them,

21
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,210
come get them yourself.

22
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:22,760
Go.

23
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,360
Hurry!

24
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,020
Don't blame me.

25
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:30,660
They left on their own.

26
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:39,600
Why did the Japanese tie this so tightly?

27
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:41,660
They have no respect for the elderly.

28
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,200
Mr. Wang.

29
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:49,360
It's alright now.

30
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,160
The Jiuju Sect

31
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,400
wants to use the Yellow and Willow Immortals

32
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,600
to find the source of the Peach Blossom Array's Qi,

33
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,729
break our Feng Shui,

34
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,840
and sever our nation's destiny.

35
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,520
You must stop them.

36
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,600
I know very well.

37
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,520
I won't let them succeed.

38
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:17,860
Where is Shiqi?

39
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,000
Wang Shiqi.

40
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,800
It's all your fault for letting the two immortals escape.

41
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,920
You ruined my plan.

42
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:58,130
You didn't keep an eye on them yourself, yet you blame me.

43
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,210
The dragon vein is indeed here.

44
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,920
What dragon vein?

45
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,240
It's actually just a tomb

46
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,840
with many buried treasures.

47
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,440
I think the antiques

48
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,370
Song Wencai gave to Ruyan back then

49
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,840
should be from here.

50
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:28,800
Song Ping didn't want this place to be exposed.

51
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:31,200
That's why he hurt so many innocent people.

52
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:32,680
Wang Shiqi.

53
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:35,320
With so much treasure laid out here,

54
00:03:35,640 --> 00:03:37,240
do you still want to fight me?

55
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,040
Of course not.

56
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,010
There's an old Chinese saying:

57
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,140
a wise man submits to circumstances.

58
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,320
Since...

59
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,680
Since that's the case,

60
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:52,040
I must use these treasures to buy guns and cannons,

61
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,800
and drive all you foreign devils

62
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,920
out.

63
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:55,640
You!

64
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,600
Then I will kill you,

65
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:02,540
use these treasures for military funds,

66
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,560
and use them to kill all of you.

67
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:06,920
That depends on whether they agree.

68
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,399
They are not protective spirits at all,

69
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,560
but rather

70
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:21,180
the tomb keepers here.

71
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,720
Worried about the tomb being destroyed,

72
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,120
so that day when you

73
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:30,480
recklessly damaged it,

74
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,920
they were drawn out.

75
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,200
They're your defeated foes anyway.

76
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,600
If so,

77
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,640
then no one can stop us

78
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,700
from getting all the treasures here.

79
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,280
If you put it that way,

80
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,409
I don't really mind.

81
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,480
But

82
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,930
you have to ask the owner of this coffin

83
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:48,700
if he agrees or not.

84
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:53,320
Even if I grind his bones to dust,

85
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,130
he's just a dead man.

86
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,400
What can he do to me?

87
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,280
Run!

88
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,920
How dare you ambush me with poison needles!

89
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,200
Whatever you are,

90
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,760
we've got beef now.

91
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,700
I dismantled your coffin.

92
00:05:39,520 --> 00:05:40,520
We searched the Song Mansion all night,

93
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,960
but couldn't find a trace of Wang Shiqi.

94
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,290
This is really bizarre.

95
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,040
The Song Mansion is so creepy.

96
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,300
I just feel like

97
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,480
something is lurking here.

98
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,000
Two days ago,

99
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,880
in the Song family's ancestral tomb,

100
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,600
the bones of that ancestor

101
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,080
went missing.

102
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,560
I felt a bit strange.

103
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,600
And the Jiuju Sect,

104
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:02,200
to sever the feng shui.

105
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,920
But eventually disappeared in

106
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,850
the Song Estate.

107
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,800
This makes one wonder

108
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,000
if the Song family's ancestral tomb

109
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:11,080
was meant as a cover-up from the start,

110
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:13,210
and there were never any bones inside.

111
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,200
Could this Song family's ancestral tomb

112
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:16,960
be

113
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:18,640
a decoy tomb deliberately set up?

114
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,720
The real ancestral tomb isn't actually here,

115
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:22,450
which is why there are no bones.

116
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,120
If you put it that way,

117
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:25,600
is there a place in Taohua Town

118
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,000
with better feng shui than

119
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,930
the Song family's ancestral tomb?

120
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:31,330
But such a place simply doesn't exist.

121
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:36,400
Song family ancestral tomb.

122
00:06:38,800 --> 00:06:39,920
The Song family.

123
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,400
The Yin dwelling covers the Yang dwelling.

124
00:06:43,200 --> 00:06:45,000
Could it be right under our feet?

125
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,480
If that's the case,

126
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:50,480
Wang Shiqi will be in great danger.

127
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,880
Wang Shiqi,

128
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:56,120
listen to me.

129
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,330
No matter where you are,

130
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,320
I am willing to marry you.

131
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,960
Did you hear me, Wang Shiqi?

132
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,930
Who's talking about me?

133
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:28,130
They actually use living people for sacrifices.

134
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,040
Feng Jiaojiao.

135
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,560
Slow down.

136
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,720
You stinking executioner.

137
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,600
You're finally here.

138
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,600
All right.

139
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,840
I mean,

140
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,650
how did you end up like this?

141
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,800
You're going to scare me to death, lady.

142
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,400
I don't know who I offended.

143
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,800
How did I fall

144
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,520
into this place?

145
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,600
It's too scary.

146
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:42,240
I thought you weren't coming for me.

147
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,360
Sister.

148
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,120
Sister.

149
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:53,760
I beg you.

150
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,200
My injuries haven't healed yet.

151
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,520
Don't attract that thing

152
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,600
over.

153
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,960
I can't handle it.

154
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,640
Is that thing so scary?

155
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:05,720
Even your executioner's sword can't deal with it?

156
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,920
Come out first.

157
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,450
The weird silk that old guy uses

158
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,200
is as thin as water,

159
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:19,240
specifically countering my executioner's sword.

160
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,080
I see.

161
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,480
It's just like how

162
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,280
my tenderness

163
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,760
specifically counters your invulnerability.

164
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,000
It's the same.

165
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,040
Let go.

166
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,280
I really should have left you in there.

167
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:30,840
You can't leave.

168
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:32,200
What will I do if you leave?

169
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,480
You heartless man!

170
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:34,640
It's

171
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:36,160
so scary here.

172
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,440
Look at yourself.

173
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,460
Your greed brought this upon you,

174
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,520
and you blame others.

175
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,520
I don't care anyway.

176
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,520
You have to protect me here.

177
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:44,180
Otherwise,

178
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,840
let me absorb some of your yang energy.

179
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,560
Let me!

180
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:49,040
It's every man

181
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,600
for himself.
